headline: Carnival (CCL) Stock Is Up, What You Need To Know
summary: Shares of cruise ship company Carnival (NYSE:CCL) jumped 3.9% in the afternoon session after Argus Research Company maintained its buy rating and raised its price target on the stock to $40 from $30.

headline: Norwegian Cruise Line (NCLH) Shares Skyrocket, What You Need To Know
summary: Shares of cruise company Norwegian Cruise Line (NYSE:NCLH) jumped 5.1% in the afternoon session after Stifel increased its price target on the stock to $37 from $35 while maintaining a "Buy" rating.
